&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;加權股價指數近 6 個月價量表現：&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;（資料來源：Bloomberg, 截至2023/07/05）&quot; data-height=&quot;161&quot; data-mime=&quot;image/jpeg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;4.490683229813665&quot; data-src-m=&quot;https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5240460/m/a422b687c366e86f41474689bab64781.jpg&quot; data-width=&quot;723&quot; src=&quot;https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5240460/l/a422b687c366e86f41474689bab64781.jpg&quot;&gt;
